room_title: Escape room "Project: RED" by Escape Cedar Valley in Cedar Falls
room_address: 115 E 4th Street, Suite 101 Cedar Falls, IA 50613
room_description: You've unwittingly become a participant in a secret government experiment devised during the Red Scare of the early 1950's. While it looks bleak, Dr. Eugene Powell has had an attack of conscience and left behind what you need - can you discover it before time runs out?
